  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>英雄の“黒”としてメンバー入り
おめでとうございます</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Congratulations on becoming a
member here as our "Black" hero!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>わかったよ。
やりゃあいいんだろ、やりゃあよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I get it already.
If I gotta do it, I'm just gonna get it over with.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ところで、さっきから
ユーリの事ばかり欲しがってるみたいだけど
僕はいらないのかな？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>By the way, it seems like you've only paid mind
to Yuri all this time. Do you not want my
assistance as well?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>25</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>入りたいのかよ……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You really want in on this?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>24</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>……ごめんなさい。
“黄色”はもう足りているの</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>...I'm sorry.
We already have enough "yellow"</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>9</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>…………</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>.........</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>あっ、オレ“黄色”だったんだ！！？</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Ah! "Yellow" is me?!!</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>8</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
